possibly yanni 's best original release most of yanni 's releases before this cd were compilations of earlier works . this was his first all new work in quite a while . and i still consider it his best work to date . this cd contains most of the pieces used in his & quot ; live at the acropolis & quot ; . the & quot ; live & quot ; cd and video have a better performance of these pieces however , because of the added instrumentation . but in the realm of his non-live recordings , this is his best